21:09.067 --> 21:10.534
So there I am, on Easter Island,

21:10.536 --> 21:12.603
and the heads ask me
to play them a song.

21:12.605 --> 21:14.572
I say, "Why me, heads?

21:14.574 --> 21:17.074
You've heard the music
of the universe itself."

21:17.076 --> 21:18.476
And they say, "Sammy,

21:18.478 --> 21:20.544
your stuff rocks
just a little harder."

21:20.546 --> 21:22.213
That's when I wake up.

21:22.215 --> 21:24.582
I'm in the Springfield
Elementary parking lot,

21:24.584 --> 21:28.085
doing a buck fifty-five
in my Ferrari 512 Boxer.

21:28.087 --> 21:29.420
I was cornering so hard,

21:29.422 --> 21:31.088
I blacked out
from the Gs, man.

21:31.090 --> 21:33.324
They say I ran over
the groundskeeper.

21:33.326 --> 21:35.092
Probably get life in prison.

21:35.094 --> 21:36.427
But I got a plan to escape,

21:36.429 --> 21:38.095
using only this harmonica

21:38.097 --> 21:40.097
and some guitar picks
with my face on 'em.

21:40.099 --> 21:42.166
Who's with me on this?

21:48.106 --> 21:50.174
(Hagar laughing)
